  "title": "Create a light version without bundled dependencies",
  "body": "We could do this:\n- expose instantsearch.react/lodash/hogan => allow people building widgets reusing our dependencies\n- declare react/lodash/hogan/algoliasearch/algoliasearch-helper as externals in a new build named instantsearch.without.deps[.min].js\n  - this would mean that the user would have to include react/lodash/hogan/algoliasearch/.. in his own webpage\n",
